                                        <br>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>কারণ, V বাড়লে T বাড়ে&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-11-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-132" style="width: 3.609em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.953em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1002.87em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-133"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-134"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-135" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-136"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-137" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-138" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-139" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-140" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-11">\rm \left(V\propto T\right)</script></span> একই চাপের জন্য।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 3</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি গ্যাসের অণু <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-12-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-141" style="width: 2.908em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.386em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1002.35em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-142"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-143"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.977em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.97em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-144"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-145"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-146" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.395em; left: 1.008em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-147"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-148"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-149" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-150" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-151" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.184em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-12">\rm {10}^{-3}s</script></span> সময়ে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-18-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03BB;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>7</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mn>1200</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5.83</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>7</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-218" style="width: 11.764em; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

font-family: MathJax_Main;">273</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-313" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-314" style="font-size: 70.7%; top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.42em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-315" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-316" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">96.43</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-317" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>35</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>96.43</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-22">\rm PV=n_1RT_1=n_2RT_2\ \therefore\frac{n_1}{n_2}=\frac{T_2}{T_1}=\frac{273+24}{273+35}=96.43\%</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3.7</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-318" style="width: 13.609em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.15em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1011.11em, 2.789em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-319"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-320" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-321" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">%</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-322" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-323" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-324" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.051em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.486em, 1001.93em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -4.506em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.982em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-325"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-326"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-327" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-328" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-329" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-330"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-331" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-332" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.7em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-333"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-334" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-335" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.05em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.051em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-336" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-337" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.7em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -4.506em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-338"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-339" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-340" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.7em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.686em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-341"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.699em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-342" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-344" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-345" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-346" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-347" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">3.7</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-348" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.597em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3.7</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-23">\rm \therefore\%n=\frac{n_2-n_1}{n_1}=\frac{n_2}{n_1}-1=3.7\%</script></span></p>

<p>এখানে চার্লসের সূত্র খাটিয়ে অঙ্ক করলে উত্তর মিলবে। কিন্তু পদ্ধতিগতভাবে সঠিক হবে না। কারণ ভরের পরিবর্তন হয়েছে বিধায় চার্লসের সূত্র প্রযোজ্য নয়।</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                            <span>Question 5</span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি সিলিন্ডারে রাখা একটি আদর্শ গ্যাসের অণুগুলোর বর্গমূল-গড়-বর্গবেগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-24-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>u</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-349" style="width: 0.71em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.561em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1000.52em, 2.312em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-350"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-351" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">u</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.2em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.639em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>u</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-24">u</script></span>। গ্যাসে তাপ প্রয়োগের ফলে চাপ 9&nbsp;গুণ বৃদ্ধি পেল। সিলিন্ডারের আয়তন অপরিবর্তিত থাকলে গ্যাসের অণুগুলোর পরিবর্তিত বর্গমূল-গড়-বর্গবেগ কত?</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mo accent=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x00AF;</mo></mover></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mfrac><mover><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup><mo accent=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x00AF;</mo></mover><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x00AF;</mo></mover></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn><mo>;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mover><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>c</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot;                                         <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 6</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো একদিন হাইগ্রোমিটারের শুষ্ক ও সিক্ত বাল্বের পাঠ যথাক্রমে&nbsp;28°C এবং 24°C পাওয়া গেল। 28°C তাপমাত্রায় গ্লেইসারের রাশির মান 1.67 হলে শিশিরাঙ্ক-&nbsp;</p>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-503" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.281em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-506" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.371em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-507" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-508" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-509" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-510" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">28</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-511" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-512" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">1.67</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-513" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-514" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-515" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-516"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-517" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">28</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-518" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-519" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">24</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-520" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-521" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-522" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">21.32</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-523"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-524"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-525" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">°</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-526" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">G</mi><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>28</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1.67</mn><mo>×</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>28</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>24</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>21.32</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-28">\rm t=t_1-G\left(t_1-t_2\right)=28-1.67\times\left(28-24\right)=21.32°C </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-29-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-527" style="width: 16.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.486em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1013.49em, 2.707em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-528"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-529" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-531" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-532" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-533" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.66em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.658em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-534" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-535" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-536" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-537" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.314em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.58em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.285em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-538" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.15em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.572em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-539"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-540" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-541" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">M</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.31em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.314em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-542" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-543" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-544" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-545" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.568em, 1000.37em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-546" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ρ</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.326em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-547" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">M</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.78em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-548" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-549" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-550" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-551" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-552" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">∝</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-553" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">ρ</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi></mrow></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>ρ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>∝</mo><mi>ρ</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-29">\rm P=\frac{n}{V}RT=\frac{m}{VM}RT=\frac{\rho}{M}RT\therefore P\propto \rho </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 8</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো দ্বিপারমাণবিক গ্যাসের প্রতিটি অণুর গড়শক্তি <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-30-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></msup><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-554" style="width: 3.839em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.132em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.269em, 1003.09em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-555"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-556"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.349em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute;                                             <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">B</span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>দ্বিপারমাণবিক গ্যাসের অণুর স্বাধীনতার মাত্রা&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-35-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-618" style="width: 1.559em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.273em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.232em, 1001.23em, 2.174em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-619"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-620" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-621" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-35">\rm = 5</script></span></p>

width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mn>5</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>20</mn></mrow></msup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>21</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-36">\rm \therefore\frac{5}{2}KT={10}^{-20}\Rightarrow5\times\frac{1}{2}KT={10}^{-20}\Rightarrow\frac{1}{2}KT=2\times{10}^{-21}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 9</span>
                                        </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-747" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-748" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">31.02</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-749" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi>ρ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>101325</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>31.02</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-38">\rm \Rightarrow h=\frac{3P_2}{\rho g}\Rightarrow h=\frac{3\times101325}{1000\ \times9.8}=31.02m</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 10</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নির্দিষ্ট পরিমাণ ভরের ও আয়তনের একটি গ্যাসের আদি চাপ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-39-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-750" style="width: 1.38em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.12em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.12em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-751"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-752"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.12em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.206em, 1000.63em, 4.1em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-753" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.673em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-754" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.2em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.093em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-39">\rm P_1 </script></span> বনাম পরিবর্তিত চাপ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-40-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-755" style="width: 1.38em;                                     <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>53.13</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-776" style="width: 12.584em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-804"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-805"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.904em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; width: 0px; height: 2.83em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>;</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1.68</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-55">\rm n_1T_1=n_2T_2\Rightarrow\frac{n_2}{n_1}=\frac{T_1}{T_2};  \%\ Change =\frac{n_1-n_2}{n_1}=\left(1-\frac{T_1}{T_2}\right)=1.68\%</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>এখানে,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1048" style="width: 11.477em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.387em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.273em, 1009.39em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1049"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1050"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1051" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">n</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.576em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1052" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1053" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1054" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">16</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1055" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1056" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1057" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1058" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1059" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1060" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1061" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1062" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">l</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1063" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1064" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1065" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1066"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1067" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1068" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.247em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-63">\rm n^2=16\therefore n=4\ mole\ CO_2</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-68-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>40</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1093" style="width: 9.879em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.076em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1007.91em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1094"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1095"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.203em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1096" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1097" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1098" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1099" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.6em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.465em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.818em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1100"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1101" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1102" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1103" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">32</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1104" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">9</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.76em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1105" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1106" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">x</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1107" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1108" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1109" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">40</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1110"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1111"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1112" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">°</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">x</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-68">\rm \frac{x}{5}=\frac{x-32}{9}\Rightarrow x =-40° </script></span></p>

<p>SI&nbsp;স্কেল&nbsp;→&nbsp;কেলভিন স্কেল।</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-69-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>273</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>233</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1113" style="width: 10.371em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.486em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.395em, 1008.45em, 2.42em, -999.998em); top: -2.211em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1114"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1115" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1116" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">T</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1117" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1118" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">273</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1119" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1120" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">40</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1121" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1122" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">233</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1123" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">K</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.148em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.052em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>273</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>233</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-69">\rm \therefore T=273-40=233K</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1153" style="width: 18.199em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.92em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.863em, 1014.92em, 2.543em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1154"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1155" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1156" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1157" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">J</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1158" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1159" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1160" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1161" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1162" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1163" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1164" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">J</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1165" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1166" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1167" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">S</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1168" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1169" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1170" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1171" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1172" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1173" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1174" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.863em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.74em, 4.305em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1175"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1176" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1177" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1178"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1179" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1180" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">S</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.86em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.863em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.547em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">S</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">S</mi></mrow></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-74">\rm W=JH\Rightarrow mgh=J\times mS\Delta\theta\Rightarrow\Delta\theta=\frac{gh}{JS}</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-75-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mn>9.8</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>50</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>4.2</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1000</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0.1167</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1181" style="width: 8.609em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 7.051em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1007.01em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1182"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1183"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.994em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1002.13em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.064em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1184"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1185" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">50</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.83em, 4.141em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1192" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1193" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-81-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1.176</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1249" style="width: 4.283em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.509em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.323em, 1003.46em, 2.325em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1250"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1251" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1.176</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1252"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1253"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1254" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">°</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1255" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.053em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.003em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1.176</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-81">\rm 1.176°C </script></span></p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-82-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.235</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1256" style="width: 16.273em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.322em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1013.28em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1257"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1258"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1259" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1260" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1261" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1262"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1263" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.535em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1264" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1265" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1266" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.29em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1267" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1268" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.494em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1269" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1270" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1271" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">S</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1272" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1273" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1274" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1275" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1276" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">θ</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1277" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">S</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi>θ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.235</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-82">\rm \frac{1}{2}mv^2\times\frac{1}{5}=mS\Delta\theta\Rightarrow\Delta\theta=0.235°C </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 16</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>0°C তাপমাত্রার 80g&nbsp;পানিকে 100°C&nbsp;তাপমাত্রায় নেয়া হলে কী পরিমাণ এনট্রপি বৃদ্ধি পাবে?</p>

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
