                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-93-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>800</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1394" style="width: 3.418em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.78em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.368em, 1002.74em, 2.416em, -999.998em); top: -2.184em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1395"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1396" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1397" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">800</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1398" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.188em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.164em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.058em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>−</mo><mn>800</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-93">\rm -800J</script></span></p>
</label>
                                                <span class="fas fa-check"></span>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-94-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>U</mi><mo>+</mo><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>500</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>300</mn><mo>+</mo><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>800</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1399" style="width: 24.961em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-99-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>=</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B3;</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>0.6</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.67</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1438" style="width: 12.502em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.248em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1010.25em, 2.379em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1439"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1440" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1441" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1442" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1443" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">γ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1444" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1445" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1446" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1447"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1448" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1449" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.6</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1450" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1451" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1452" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">γ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1453" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1454" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1.67</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-100-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1455" style="width: 0.658em;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>A ইঞ্জিন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-101-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>400</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1458" style="width: 2.796em;                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 20</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি কার্নো ইঞ্জিনের দক্ষতা 20%&nbsp;এবং তাপ গ্রাহকের তাপমাত্রা 127°C। দক্ষতা 50% করতে হলে তাপ উৎসের তাপমাত্রা কত বাড়াতে হবে?</p>

                                        </div>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-106-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>500</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1525" style="width: 13.773em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 11.273em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1011.23em, 2.625em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1526"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1527" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1528" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1529" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1531" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.789em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.67em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.465em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.35em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1532"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1533" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.79em, 1.191em, -999.998em); <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-107-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; </span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 21</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি রেফ্রিজারেটরের কর্মসম্পাদন সহগ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-108-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5.4</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1590" style="width: 1.567em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1001.23em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1591"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1592" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">5.4</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.957em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>5.4</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-108">\rm 5.4 </script></span> এবং প্রতি চক্রে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-109-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>81</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1593" style="width: 1.865em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.529em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1001.49em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1594"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1595" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">81</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1596" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-114-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi></mfrac><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>v</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mo>,</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>u</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>p</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>l</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>d</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>e</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1613" style="width: 18.732em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.33em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1015.21em, 2.502em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1617" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.986em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.7em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1621" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">W</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.99em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1627" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1628" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1629" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">r</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1630" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1631" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1632" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1633" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">v</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1634" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1635" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1636" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1637" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1638" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1640" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1641" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">,</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1642" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.166em;">W</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1643" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1644" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1645" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">u</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1646" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1647" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">p</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1648" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">l</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1649" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">i</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1650" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1651" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">d</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1652" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1653" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">h</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1654" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">e</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1655" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1656" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1657" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">]</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi></mfrac><mrow><mo>[</mo><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">v</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mo>,</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">u</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">p</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">i</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">d</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">e</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi></mrow><mo>]</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-114">\rm K=\frac{Q_1}{W}\left[Q_1\ removed\ heat , W\ supplied\ heat\right]</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-115-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5.4</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>81</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>437.4</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1658" style="width: 15.822em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.953em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1012.91em, 2.338em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1659"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1660" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1661" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.74em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1662" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">Q</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.781em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1663" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1664" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1665" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">K</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1666" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1667" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">W</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1668" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1669" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">5.4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1670" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1671" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">81</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1672" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1673" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">437.4</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1674" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.297em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>5.4</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>81</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>437.4</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-115">\rm \Rightarrow Q_1=K\times W=5.4\times81=437.4J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                            <p>একটি তাপগতীয় প্রত্যাবর্তী প্রক্রিয়ার&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-120-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1695" style="width: 3.243em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.647em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.61em, 2.424em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1696"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1697" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1698" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">−</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1699" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.225em;">V</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.134em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.048em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>−</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-120">\rm P-V</script></span>&nbsp;লেখচিত্রটি সামান্তরিকের মতো দেখতে। কৃতকাজ কত?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>সামান্তরিকের ক্ষেত্রফলই কৃতকাজ,&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-124-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>|</mo><mover><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>D</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>A</mi></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2192;</mo></mover><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>j</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1715" style="width: 11.6em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.51em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.641em, 1009.51em, 4.1em, -999.998em); position: relative; width: 0.289em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; font-family: MathJax_Main; top: -3.277em; left: 0em;">∣<span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1743"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1744"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1745" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">|</span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1746" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-125-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>|</mo><mover><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>D</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow><mo>&amp;#x2192;</mo></mover><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>|</mo><mrow><mn>7</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mover><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>i</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x005E;</mo></mover></mrow></mrow><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>7</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1751" style="width: 6.846em; <p>সামান্তরিকের ক্ষেত্রফল&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-127-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>135</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1781" style="width: 11.518em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1782"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1783" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1784" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; <p>তাই, কৃতকাজ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-128-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1802" style="width: 2.051em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.682em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1001.64em, 2.133em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1803"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1804" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1805" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">14</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.048em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-128">\rm =14</script></span></p>
</span>

                                            <p>মোলার তাপধারণ ক্ষমতার সমীকরণ- [m হচ্ছে মোলসংখ্যা]</p>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 25</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি টায়ারের ভেতরের চাপ হঠাৎ করেই নিঃশেষ হয়, যখন তা ফেটে যায়। এটা কী ধরনের প্রক্রিয়া?</p>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি কার্নো রেফ্রিজারেটরের অভ্যন্তরীণ তাপমাত্রা 255K এবং পরিবেশের তাপমাত্রা 303K। কার্যসম্পাদন সহগ-</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>255</mn><mrow><mn>303</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>255</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>5.31</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-41" style="width: 16.232em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.281em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.822em, 1013.2em, 2.666em, -999.998em);                             <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 29</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>A&nbsp;ইঞ্জিন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-9-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>400</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-116" style="width: 2.796em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.275em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.24em, 2.386em, -999.998em);                                     <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 30</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি তাপগতীয় প্রত্যাবর্তী প্রক্রিয়ার P-V লেখচিত্রটি সামান্তরিকের মতো দেখতে। কৃতকাজ কত?</p>

top: -1.965em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-258"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-259"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.518em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-263" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>135</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">o</mi></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-19">\rm {135}^o</script></span>&nbsp;</p>

<p>সামান্তরিকের ক্ষেত্রফল&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-20-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mn>2</mn></msqrt><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>7</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>sin</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>135</mn></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-264" style="width: 11.518em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.428em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1009.39em, 2.297em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-265"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-266" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-267" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2</span><span class="msqrt" id="MathJax-Span-268"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0.822em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-269"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-270" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.609em, 1000.49em, 3.895em, -999.998em); top: -4.547em; left: 0.822em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.055em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-271" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-272" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">7</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-273" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-274" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: relative; width: 1.928em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1001.44em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-279"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-280"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-281" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">135</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 1.518em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-282" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">o</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-283" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-284" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; <p>তাই, কৃতকাজ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-21-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-285" style="width: 2.625em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.133em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.191em, 1002.09em, 2.174em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-286"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-287" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-288" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">14</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-289" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.953em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>14</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-21">\rm =14J</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 32</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো স্থানের তাপমাত্রা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-24-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>22</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-319" style="width: 2.759em; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>22</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-24">\rm 22°C</script></span> ও আপেক্ষিক আর্দ্রতা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>52</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-326" style="width: 2.237em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-31-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>F</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>9.989</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-373" style="width: 18.732em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 15.33em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.986em, 1015.33em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-374"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-375" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-376" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-377" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.576em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.25em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.121em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-378" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.244em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-379" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.58em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.576em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-380" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-381" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">100</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-382" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-383" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-384" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.084em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-385" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-386" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.641em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1001.52em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.777em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-387"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-388" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-389" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-390" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">F</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-391" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">100</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.64em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.641em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-392" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-393" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">9.989</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-394" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-395" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-396" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-397" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-398" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-399" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">F</mi></mrow><mn>100</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>9.989</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-31">\rm R=\frac{f}{F}\times100\%\Rightarrow f=\frac{R\times F}{100}=9.989\ mm\ Hg</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 33</span>
                                           
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো গ্যাসাণু 2s সময়ে 15 cm দূরত্ব অতিক্রম করে এবং এ সময়ে এটি 24000 টি ধাক্কা খায়। গ্যাসাণুটির গড় মুক্তপথ-</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">A</span>
                                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 34</span>
                                           
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-37-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-483" style="width: 2.088em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.716em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.64em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-484"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-485" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-486"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-487"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-488" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">°</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-489" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-37">\rm 0°C</script></span> তাপমাত্রায় 3kg বরফকে <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-38-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>100</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-490" style="width: 3.318em; top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-571" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-572" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.82em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.408em;"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-573"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-574" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-575" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.95em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-576" style="vertical-align: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Size2;">]</span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.83em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">f</mi></msub></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">l</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mrow><mo>[</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>]</mo></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-43">\rm \Delta s=\Delta s_1+\Delta s_2=\frac{ml_f}{T}+msln\left[\frac{T_2}{T_1}\right] </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-44-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>3.36</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><mn>273</mn></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>4200</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>[</mo><mfrac><mn>373</mn><mn>273</mn></mfrac><mo>]</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>7624.85</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-577" style="width: 21.477em;                                             <span>Question 35</span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি বুদবুদ কোনো হ্রদের তলদেশ থেকে উপরে আসায় এর আয়তন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-45-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2.5</mn></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-616" style="width: 1.567em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.269em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1001.23em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-617"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-618" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">2.5</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>2.5</mn></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-45">\rm 2.5</script></span> গুণ হয়। হ্রদের তলদেশ ও বায়ুমণ্ডলের তাপমাত্রা সমান হলে হ্রদের গভীরতা-</p>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-50-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.5</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-635" style="width: 28.035em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-636"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-637"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-643" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-644" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-646" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-647"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-650" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-651" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-652" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-653"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-654"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-656" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-657" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-658" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-667" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-668" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-672" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-673" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-674" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">+</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-675" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">h</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-676" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">ρ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-677" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">g</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-678" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-679" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">2.5</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-680"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.109em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.199em, 1000.62em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-681" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.699em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-682" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi>ρ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><mn>2.5</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>+</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mi>ρ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2.5</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-50">\rm P_1V_1=P_2V_2\Rightarrow\left(P_2+h\rho g\right)V=P_2\times 2.5V\Rightarrow P_2+h\rho g=2.5P_2</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-51-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.5</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03C1;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.5</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>101325</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>15.51</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-683" style="width: 17.174em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-684"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-685" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-686" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-697" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-698" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-710" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-711" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.902em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.5</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><mrow><mi>ρ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">g</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1.5</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>101325</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>1000</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>×</mo><mn>9.8</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>15.51</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-51">\rm \Rightarrow h=\frac{1.5P_2}{\rho g}\Rightarrow h=\frac{1.5\times101325}{1000\ \times9.8}=15.51m</script></span></p>
</span>

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 36</span>
                                           
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>কোনো গতিশীল বস্তু হঠাৎ থেমে যাওয়ায় তাপমাত্রা <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-52-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>3</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#xB0;</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-713" style="width: 2.088em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.716em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.418em, 1001.64em, 2.386em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-714"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-715" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-716"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-717"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-718" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">°</span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-719" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">C</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>3</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>°</mo></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-52">\rm 3°C</script></span> বেড়ে গেল। এর উপাদানের আপেক্ষিক তাপ&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.076em, 1000.86em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.096em; left: 0em;"><span style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">√</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-806" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-807" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">68.41</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-808" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-809" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-810"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-811" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-812"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-813"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-814" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-815" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-63-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>500</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-830" style="width: 13.773em; top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-831"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-832" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">0.2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-833" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>0.2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>500</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-63">\rm 0.2=1-\frac{273+127}{T_1}\Rightarrow T_1=500K</script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-64-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>0.4</mn><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msubsup></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msubsup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn><mi class=&quot;MJX-variant&quot; mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x2032;</mi></msubsup><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>666.67</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>500</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>166.67</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-851" style="width: 33.035em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 27.051em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.945em, 1027.01em, 2.748em, -999.998em);                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-71-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03B3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mrow><mi>&amp;#x03B3;</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-936" style="width: 9.551em;                                                 <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-74-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>2</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-989" style="width: 5.786em; padding-left: 0.276em;">=</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-995" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.276em;">R</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-996" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span></span><span style="display: inline-block;
