</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">
                                                <span class="input-group-text">C</span>

</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 41</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>যে তাপমাত্রায় ফারেনহাইট ও কেলভিন স্কেল একই মান প্রদর্শন করে তা হল-</p>

                                        </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 42</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>হ্রদের তলদেশ থেকে উপরে আসায় বায়ু বুদবুদের ব্যাস 3 গুণ হলো। হ্রদের উপরে চাপ <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-84-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>1</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1140" style="width: 3.02em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.461em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.455em, 1002.46em, 2.349em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1141"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1142" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1143" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1144" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1145" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1146" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.043em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 0.911em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mn>1</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-84">\rm 1\ atm</script></span> হলে হ্রদের গভীরতা কত?</p>

width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.72em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 1.723em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1220" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1221" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">4.167</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1222" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1223" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">a</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1224" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">t</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1225" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">m</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-1226" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1227" style="font-family: MathJax_AMS; padding-left: 0.289em;">∴</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1228" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">Δ</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1229" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1230" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1231" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.256em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1002.13em, 4.264em, -999.998em); top: -4.506em; left: 50%; margin-left: -1.064em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1232"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1233"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1234" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1235" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1236" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1237"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1238" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0.781em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.45em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1241" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">P</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1242" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1002.26em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.256em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1243" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1244" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">100</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1245" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1246" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1247" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">66.67</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1248" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>4.167</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>∴</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">Δ</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>66.67</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-92">\rm P_2=\frac{P_1V_1}{V_2}=4.167\ atm\ \therefore\Delta P=\frac{P_2-P_1}{P_1}\times100\% 
=66.67\% 
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 44</span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-99-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>t</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi>&amp;#x03B8;</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>tan</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>53.13</mn><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>;</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1275" style="width: 16.764em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 13.732em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1013.73em, 2.625em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1276"><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-1277"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; position: relative; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1279" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 2.215em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.852em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>∴</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>33.3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mo>≈</mo><mn>33</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-100">\rm \therefore\frac{P_2}{P_1}=\frac{4}{3}   \therefore\frac{P_2-P_1}{P_1}=\frac{4-3}{3}\times100=33.3\%\approx33\%</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-105-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1412" style="width: 2.953em; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.66em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.658em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>∝</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mfrac></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-105">\rm P\propto\frac{1}{V}</script></span>; তাই, P বাড়লে V কমবে। [একই তাপমাত্রার জন্য]</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-113-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>r</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>s</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mrow><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub></mfrac></msqrt><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>N</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>5222</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>4949</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>o</mi></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1475" style="width: 23.732em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-118-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>E</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>1.38</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>23</mn></mrow></msup><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>120</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1599" style="width: 19.059em; <p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-119-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>8.14</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>21</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1631" style="width: 6.928em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 5.658em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1005.62em, 2.174em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1632"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1633" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1634" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">8.14</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1635" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-1636" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 2.338em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1637"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1638"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1639" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1640"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1641"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1642" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1643" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">21</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1644" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>8.14</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>21</mn></mrow></msup><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-119">\rm =8.14\times{10}^{-21}J</script></span>&nbsp;[দ্বিপরমাণুক হলেও রৈখিক স্বাধীনতার মাত্রা তিন]</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 49</span>
                                            
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি তাপগতীয় প্রক্রিয়ায় অন্তঃস্থ শক্তির পরিবর্তন শূন্য হলে, প্রক্রিয়াটি হবে-</p>

                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row questionOptions">
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">

                                                <label style="margin-left:5px;"><p>সমচাপ প্রক্রিয়া</p>
</label>
                                                
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group " style="align-items: center;">

</label>
                                                
                                            </div>

                                            </div>
                                        </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>অন্তঃস্থ শক্তির পরিবর্তন শূন্য মানে তাপমাত্রার পরিবর্তন শূন্য। তাই সমোষ্ণ প্রক্রিয়া</p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>

display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 10.781em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1010.74em, 2.502em, -999.998em); </span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 52</span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নির্দিষ্ট ভরের একটি আদর্শ গ্যাসের আয়তন ধ্রুব চাপে দ্বিগুণ করা হল। যদি গ্যাসের প্রাথমিক তাপমাত্রা&nbsp;10°C&nbsp;হয় তবে চূড়ান্ত তাপমাত্রা কত?</p>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-150-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><mi>V</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>V</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>283</mn></mrow><mi>V</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>566</mn><mi>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4123" style="width: 17.953em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.715em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.109em, 1014.72em, 2.83em, -999.998em); \frac{V_1}{T_1}=\ \frac{V_2}{T_2}\therefore T_2=\frac{V_2\times T_1}{V}=\ \frac{2V\times283}{V}=566K

padding-left: 0.289em;">10</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4355" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">c</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4356" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">m</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>π</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>40</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>127</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>π</mi><msup><mi>r</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>40</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow></mrow><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>227</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn><mi>c</mi><mi>m</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-164">\frac{V_1}{T_1}=\frac{V_2}{T_2}\Rightarrow\frac{\pi r^2\times40}{273+127}=\frac{\pi r^2\left(40+x\right)}{273+227}\Rightarrow x=10cm</script></span></p>
</span>

                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-169-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>C</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>22</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>C</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><msup><mn>30</mn><mi>o</mi></msup><mi>C</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4384" style="width: 18.527em; margin-left: -1.268em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-4398"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4399" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4400" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4404" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-4405" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.658em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.53em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.285em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4406" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4407" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">5</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.66em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.658em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4408" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">⇒</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4409" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.289em;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4410" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4411" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4412" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-4413" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4416" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">C<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.702em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>C</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>22</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>32</mn></mrow><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>C</mi><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>C</mi><mo>=</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>−</mo><msup><mn>30</mn><mi>o</mi></msup><mi>C</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-169">\frac{F-32}{9}=\frac{C}{5}\Rightarrow\frac{-22-32}{9}=\frac{C}{5}\Rightarrow C=\ -30^oC </script></span></p>

<p>কেলভিন স্কেলে&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-170-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>30</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>273</mn></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>243</mn><mi>K</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4417" style="width: 10.084em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 8.24em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.15em, 1008.24em, 2.379em, -999.998em); padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4429" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">243</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4430" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">K<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; </span>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-172-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mrow><mo>|</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>|</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>P</mi><mi>V</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>n</mi><mi>R</mi><mi>T</mi></mrow><msup><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x2234;</mo><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mrow><mo>|</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>d</mi><mi>V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>|</mo></mrow><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>&amp;#x221D;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><msup><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-4450" style="width: 14.469em; vertical-align: -0.847em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.302em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><mi>W</mi><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>−</mo><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mi>W</mi><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>46000</mn><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>273</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>27</mn></mrow><mn>373</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>≈</mo><mn>9003</mn><mi>J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-178">\frac{W}{Q_1}=\frac{Q_1-Q_2}{Q_1}=1-\frac{Q_2}{Q_1}=1-\frac{T_2}{T_1}\Rightarrow W=Q_1\left(1-\frac{T_2}{T_1}\right)=46000\left(1-\frac{273+27}{373}\right)\approx9003J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>

width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-4751" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-4752" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">203.9</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-4753" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-4754" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">K<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.043em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 5.453em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -3.748em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 5.553em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msubsup><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn><mi>γ</mi></msubsup><msubsup><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow></msubsup><mo>=</mo><msubsup><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn><mi>γ</mi></msubsup><msubsup><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow><mi>γ</mi></mfrac></mrow></msubsup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msubsup><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow><mi>γ</mi></mfrac></mrow></msubsup><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mi>γ</mi></mrow><mi>γ</mi></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>303</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>1</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mn>1.4</mn></mrow><mn>1.4</mn></mfrac></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>203.9</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi>K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-182">T_1^ \gamma P_1^{1-\gamma} =T_2^\gamma P_2^{1-\gamma} \Rightarrow T_1P_1^{\frac{1-\gamma}{\gamma}}=T_2P_2^{\frac{1-\gamma}{\gamma}}\\
T_2=T_1\times\left(\frac{P_1}{P_2}\right)^\frac{1-\gamma}{\gamma}=303\times\left(\frac{4}{1}\right)^\frac{1-1.4}{1.4}=203.9\ K </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 61</span>

vertical-align: -0.348em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.453em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>–</mo><msub><mi>V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo stretchy="false">(</mo><mn>9.496</mn><mo>–</mo><mn>1</mn><mo stretchy="false">)</mo><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-202">=V_2–V_1=(9.496–1) \times 10^{-3} m^3 </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-203-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mn>8.496</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2013;</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>8.496</mn><mi>L</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-5158" style="width: 11.969em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 9.797em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1009.76em, 2.174em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5159"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5160" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5161" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">8.496</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5162" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-5163" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.764em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.24em, 1000.95em, 4.182em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5164" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">10</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.424em; left: 0.986em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-5165"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-5166"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5167" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">–</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5168" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-5169"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.863em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5171" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5172" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-5173" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.098em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.203em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mn>8.496</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mn>10</mn><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>–</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup><msup><mi>m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>8.496</mn><mi>L</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-203">= 8.496\times10^{–3}m^3=8.496L</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p>মোট গতিশক্তি&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-6-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>n</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mfrac><mn>52</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>310</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6045</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-30" style="width: 17.912em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 14.674em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1014.63em, 2.502em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-31"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-32" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-33" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-34" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-35" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.49em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-41" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.494em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">3</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-44" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">×</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-45" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; margin-left: -0.367em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-46" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">52</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.33em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -3.645em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.162em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-47" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">4</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1000.82em, 1.191em, -999.998em); top: -1.268em; left: 0em;"><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 0.822em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-48" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-53" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">6045</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-54" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">R</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-55" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-56" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">J</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.497em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.602em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">n</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mfrac><mn>52</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mo>×</mo><mn>310</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6045</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">J</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-6">\rm =\frac{3}{2}\ nRT=\frac{3}{2}\times\frac{52}{4}\times R\times310=6045R\ J</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                            <span>Question 70</span>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>নিচের কোনটি প্রত্যাগামী রুদ্ধতাপীয় প্রক্রিয়ার ক্ষেত্রে প্রযোজ্য?</p>

                                            <span>Question 72</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>একটি কার্নো ইঞ্জিন যখন 27°C তাপমাত্রার তাপগ্রাহকে থাকে তখন এর কর্মদক্ষতা 50%। তাপ উৎসের তাপমাত্রা 150°C বৃদ্ধি করলে কর্মদক্ষতা-</p>

                                        </div>

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-22-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi>&amp;#x03B7;</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>300</mn><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>H</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>600</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-333" style="width: 15.125em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 12.379em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.027em, 1012.3em, 2.625em, -999.998em); top: -2.006em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-334"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-335"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0.945em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.49em, 4.346em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-336" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">η<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.002em;"></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-337" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-338" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-339" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">0.5</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-340" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-341" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-342" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.191em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1001.03em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -0.531em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-344" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">300</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.95em, 4.264em, -999.998em); clip: rect(3.404em, 1000.49em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-346" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">T</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.891em; left: 0.494em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-347" style="font-size: 50%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.19em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.85em; left: 0.74em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-351" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">H</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-352" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-353" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">600</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-354" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">K</span><span class="mtext" id="MathJax-Span-355" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">&nbsp;</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-356" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">;</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.647em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.752em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi>η</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.5</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>300</mn><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">H</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>600</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-22">\rm \eta_1=0.5=1-\frac{300}{T_H}\Rightarrow T_H=600K\ ; </script></span></p>

<p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-23-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi>&amp;#x03B7;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mfrac><mn>300</mn><mn>750</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>450</mn><mn>750</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>60</mn><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0025;</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-357" style="width: 13.076em; padding-left: 0.289em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-362" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.207em;">−</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-363" style="padding-left: 0.207em;"><span style="display: inline-block;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-30-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B8;</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>&amp;#x21D2;</mo><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>h</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mo>&amp;#x2206;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x3B8;</mo></mrow></mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>g</mi></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>4200</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mn>40</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>840</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>m</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-484" style="width: 19.51em; </span>
                                    </div>

                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p>37°C তাপমাত্রায় <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-5-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msub><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-40" style="width: 1.455em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1001.19em, 2.461em, -999.998em); top: -2.196em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-41"><span class="msubsup" id="MathJax-Span-42"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.194em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.169em, 1000.71em, 4.137em, -999.998em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-43" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">O</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -3.836em; left: 0.784em;"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-44" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.988em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.2em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.225em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.139em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-5">\rm O_2</script></span> অণুর মূল গড় বর্গ বেগের মান কত?</p>

position: relative; width: 1.355em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.445em, 1000.37em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.014em; left: 0em;"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-133" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">s</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.383em; left: 0.412em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-134"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-135"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-136" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-137" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">1</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 2.402em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">r</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>310</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></mfrac></msqrt><mo>=</mo><mn>491.55</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">s</mi><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-10">\rm C_{rms}=\sqrt{\frac{3RT}{M}}=\sqrt{\frac{3\times8.314\times310}{32\times{10}^{-3}}}=491.55\ ms^{-1} </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 78</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
একটি কার্নো ইঞ্জিনের কার্যকর বস্তু 450K তাপমাত্রার উৎস হতে 850J তাপ গ্রহণ করে শীতল আধারে 550J তাপ বর্জন করে।</p>

                                </div>

padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-343" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">35.29</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-344" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">%</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.469em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -2.897em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>η</mi><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mrow><mo>(</mo><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>−</mo><mfrac><mn>550</mn><mn>850</mn></mfrac></mrow><mo>)</mo></mrow><mo>×</mo><mn>100</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>35.29</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">%</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-23">\rm \eta=\left(1-\frac{Q_2}{Q_1}\right)\times100\%  \\
=\left(1-\frac{550}{850}\right)\times100\%=35.29\%  
</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

vertical-align: 0em; border-top: 1.5px solid; width: 2.789em; height: 0px;"></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-384" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 4.103em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><mfrac><mn>550</mn><mn>850</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mn>450</mn></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>550</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>450</mn></mrow><mn>850</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>291.17</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-24">\rm \frac{Q_2}{Q_1}=\frac{T_2}{T_1}\Rightarrow\frac{550}{850}=\frac{T_2}{450}  \\
\Rightarrow T_2=\frac{550\times450}{850}=291.17K </script></span></p>
</span>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">

                            <div class="row question">
                                <div class="col-md-12" style="padding-left:0px; padding-right:0px;">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="serial">
                                            <span>Question 81</span>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;">বায়ুকে রুদ্ধতাপে প্রসারিত করে আয়তন 1.5 গুণ করা হলো। যদি প্রাথমিক চাপ 1 atm হয়, তবে চূড়ান্ত চাপ কত?&nbsp;<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>[</mo><mi>&amp;#x03B3;</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.4</mn><mo stretchy=&quot;false&quot;>]</mo></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-387" style="width: 4.51em; display: inline-block;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 3.69em; height: 0px; font-size: 122%;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(1.38em, 1003.58em, 2.61em, -999.998em); top: -2.234em; left: 0em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-388"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-389" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">[</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-390" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">γ<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.039em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-391" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-392" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.263em;">1.4</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-393" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">]</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.361em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.32em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mo stretchy="false">[</mo><mi>γ</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1.4</mn><mo stretchy="false">]</mo></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-25">\rm [\gamma=1.4]&nbsp;</script></span></p>

                                    <div class="col-sm-12 row questionOption">
                                        <div class="input-group" style="align-items: center;">
                                            <div class="input-group-prepend">

1.6em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-575"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-576"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-577" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-578" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">2</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 7.748em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -7.447em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 8.353em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1.5</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">t</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>101325</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn><mi>γ</mi></msubsup><mo>=</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msubsup><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn><mi>γ</mi></msubsup><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>γ</mi></msup><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mi>γ</mi></msup><mo>×</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>1.5</mn></mfrac><mo>)</mo></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>1.4</mn></mrow></msup><mo>×</mo><mn>101325</mn><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mo>=</mo><mn>5.74</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>10</mn></mrow><mn>4</mn></msup><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">N</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi></mrow><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mo>−</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-30">\rm V_2=1.5\ V_1;\ P_1=1\ atm=101325\ Pa  \\
P_1V_1^\gamma=P_2V_2^\gamma\Rightarrow\left(\frac{V_2} {V_1}\right)^\gamma=\frac{P_1}{P_2}  \\
\Rightarrow P_2=\left(\frac{V_1}{V_2}\right)^\gamma\times P_1=\left(\frac{1}{1.5}\right)^{1.4}\times101325  \\
=5.74\times{10}^4{\rm Nm}^{-2}  </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="row questionBlock">
                                <div class="row  uddipokText" style="display: block;">
                                    <p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>নিচের উদ্দীপকের আলোকে পরবর্তী দুটি প্রশ্নের উত্তর দাও:</strong><br>
<span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-1-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>25</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1" style="width: 2.61em; height: 3.988em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; top: -4.395em; left: 1.008em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-5" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">∘</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 2.237em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.089em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.002em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msup><mn>25</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-1">\rm 25^\circ{C}</script></span> তাপমাত্রা ও 1 atm চাপে একটি আদর্শ গ্যাসের আয়তন <span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;                                     </div>
                                </div>

border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 3.652em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.03</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0.09</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msup><mi mathvariant="normal">m</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>25</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>298</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>?</mo><mspace linebreak="newline"></mspace><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mfrac><mo stretchy="false">⇒</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mfrac><mo>×</mo><msub><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>0.09</mn><mn>0.03</mn></mfrac><mo>×</mo><mn>298</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>894</mn><mi mathvariant="normal">K</mi><mo>=</mo><msup><mn>621</mn><mo>∘</mo></msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mi mathvariant="normal">C</mi></mrow></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-8">\rm V_1=0.03\ m^3;\ V_2=0.09\ m^3;\ T_1=25^\circ=298K\ ;\ T_2=? \\ \frac{V_1}{T_1}=\frac{V_2}{T_2}\Rightarrow T_2=\frac{V_2}{V_1}\times T_1=\frac{0.09}{0.03}\times298=894K=621^\circ {C}</script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>

                                    <div class="row solveText" style="display: block; padding:10px; color:#077307; overflow-x: auto; background-color: #d7f7d4;">
                                        <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-25-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>&amp;#x0394;</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>S</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0.02</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>4200</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo>&amp;#x2061;</mo><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mfrac><mn>284</mn><mn>273</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>3.318</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>J</mi><msup><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>K</mi><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mo>&amp;#x2212;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-366" style="width: 17.502em;                                         <div class="questionText" style="display: block;">
                                            <p style="text-align: justify;"><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-26-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><msup><mn>127</mn><mo>&amp;#x2218;</mo></msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>C</mi></mrow></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-392" style="width: 3.243em;                                         <span style="color: black !important; font-weight: bold;">Solution:</span>
                                        <br>
                                        <span style="color: black !important;"><p><span class="math-tex"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit; display: none;"></span><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-27-Frame" tabindex="0" style="position: relative;" data-mathml="<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>W</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>R</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>M</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>16</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><mn>400</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>32</mn><mo>&amp;#x00D7;</mo><msup><mrow class=&quot;MJX-TeXAtom-ORD&quot;><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>207.85</mn><mtext>&amp;#xA0;</mtext><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>k</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>P</mi><mi mathvariant=&quot;normal&quot;>a</mi></math>" role="presentation"><nobr aria-hidden="true"><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-400" style="width: 16.477em; font-family: MathJax_Main;">V</span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 4.018em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(0.904em, 1001.89em, 1.191em, -999.998em); width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-412" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mfrac" id="MathJax-Span-413" style="padding-left: 0.289em;"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 4.592em; height: 0px; margin-right: 0.125em; margin-left: 0.125em;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.404em, 1004.47em, 4.141em, -999.998em); top: -4.424em; left: 50%; margin-left: -2.252em;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-414"><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-415" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">16</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-416" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">×</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-417" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">8.314</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-418" style="font-size: 70.7%; width: 0px; height: 1.068em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-428" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.289em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-429" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; width: 0px; height: 2.01em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; vertical-align: -0.698em; border-left: 0px solid; width: 0px; height: 1.802em;"></span></span></nobr><span class="MJX_Assistive_MathML" role="presentation"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">W</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">R</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">T</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">M</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">V</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>16</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>8.314</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>400</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>32</mn><mo>×</mo><msup><mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD"><mn>0.2</mn></mrow><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>207.85</mn><mtext>&nbsp;</mtext><mi mathvariant="normal">k</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">P</mi><mi mathvariant="normal">a</mi></math></span></span><script type="math/tex" id="MathJax-Element-27">\rm P=\frac{WRT}{MV}=\frac{16\times8.314\times400}{32\times{0.2}^3}=207.85\ kPa </script></span></p>
</span>
                                    </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
